README for vblend

See INSTALL for installation instructions.

* What is vblend?
  --------------
	vblend is a game library written in C and lua that aims to include a built-in 3D graphics editor
	with a vim/blender-like interface. 

	It is open source and cross-platform. It relies on OpenGL and the glfw framework and is intended
	to run on GNU/Linux, Mac OSX and Windows platforms.

  It is licensed under the GNU public license, version 3.
